## Tech Stack


| Layer     | Technology                                                        |
| --------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Frontend  | JavaScript, React/Vue, HTML5, CSS3, Tailwind/Bootstrap            |
| Backend   | Python (Flask/FastAPI), Node.js, Java (Spring Boot)               |
| Database  | PostgreSQL/MySQL, MongoDB, Redis                                  |
| API       | RESTful, GraphQL                                                  |
| Auth      | JWT, OAuth2, RBAC                                                 |
| AI/ML/DL  | scikit-learn, TensorFlow, PyTorch, HuggingFace Transformers       |
| Cloud     | AWS/GCP/Azure                                                     |
| DevOps    | Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD, Git                                    |
| Messaging | RabbitMQ, Kafka                                                   |
| Security  | HTTPS/TLS, input validation, rate limiting, secure key management |
